title: US 'Disinformation War' Unable to Mar Russia's Military Success in Syria
text: It seems that the new counterterrorism coalition consisting of Syria, Russia, Iraq, Iran and China has stepped in at the right moment: the world has put into question the true reason behind the US-led "phony" coalition's involvement in the Syrian conflict, US columnist Jim W. Dean underscores. ...
